%N A397744 Number of assembly trees for the n-barbell graph.
%H A397744 Andrew Howroyd, <a href="/A397744/b397744.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..100</a>
%H A397744 Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, <a href="https://mathworld.wolfram.com/AssemblyNumber.html">Assembly Number</a>.
%H A397744 Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, <a href="https://mathworld.wolfram.com/BarbellGraph.html">Barbell Graph</a>.
%F A397744 a(n) = Sum_{i=0..n-1} Sum_{j=0..n-1} binomial(i+j,i) * A193229(n-1,i) * A193229(n-1, j).
%o A397744 (PARI)
%o A397744 T(n,k) = { (2*n-k)!/(2^(n-k)*(n-k)!) } \\ A193229
%o A397744 a(n) = {sum(i=0, n-1, sum(j=0, n-1, T(n-1,i)*T(n-1,j)*binomial(i+j,i) ))}
